<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 20:07:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>那些讨厌拜登支持以色列的人最好习惯特朗普的美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/bidens-israel-stance-damaging-him-politically-but-trump-victory-will-hurt-america-more/0000018c-161c-dd2e-a5ae-d75fef930000</link><description>如果美国年轻人以加沙正义的名义袖手旁观 2024 年大选，并使美国陷入唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 毫不掩饰的法西斯主义，这更多地说明了美国严峻的政治局势，而不是乔·拜登总统的亲政。以色列的倾向</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 19:34:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/bidens-israel-stance-damaging-him-politically-but-trump-victory-will-hurt-america-more/0000018c-161c-dd2e-a5ae-d75fef930000</guid></item><item><title>布兰迪斯人权中心起诉伯克利分校反犹太主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-center-for-human-rights-sues-berkeley-for-antisemitism/0000018c-174a-dd03-a7ff-bf7af8400000</link><description>该诉讼列出了自 10 月 7 日以来，哈马斯恐怖分子从加沙渗透以色列，引发大规模军事报复以来，针对犹太学生的多起恐吓、骚扰和身体暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 19:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-center-for-human-rights-sues-berkeley-for-antisemitism/0000018c-174a-dd03-a7ff-bf7af8400000</guid></item><item><title>独自在一个房间里，受到枪威胁：被哈马斯释放的以色列儿童所经历的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/alone-in-a-room-threatened-with-a-gun-what-israeli-children-released-by-hamas-endured/0000018c-1733-dd03-a7ff-bf3b7fe00000</link><description>一名儿童不敢大声说话，另一名儿童被迫观看 10 月 7 日暴行的视频，兄弟姐妹并不知道他们的母亲已经去世</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 19:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/alone-in-a-room-threatened-with-a-gun-what-israeli-children-released-by-hamas-endured/0000018c-1733-dd03-a7ff-bf3b7fe00000</guid></item><item><title>十名女性：这些是周​​二从哈马斯手中释放的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/ten-women-these-are-the-hostages-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-tuesday/0000018c-1621-d5be-af9f-3eb92d2c0000</link><description>53 天前，十名以色列妇女从家中被绑架并带入加沙地带。作为以色列和哈马斯之间临时停火协议的一部分，他们于周二被释放</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 18:53:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/ten-women-these-are-the-hostages-freed-from-hamas-captivity-on-tuesday/0000018c-1621-d5be-af9f-3eb92d2c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方10月7日提出哈马斯恐怖分子性侵犯的新证据</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-presents-further-evidence-of-sexual-assault-by-hamas-members-on-october-7/0000018c-169e-dd03-a7ff-bebe1bdb0000</link><description>在议会特别委员会会议上，一名警方调查员展示了从 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀幸存者那里收集到的性侵犯、虐待和残害的生动证词，其中一些证词尚未公开</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 17:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-presents-further-evidence-of-sexual-assault-by-hamas-members-on-october-7/0000018c-169e-dd03-a7ff-bebe1bdb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院指控巴勒斯坦记者因 Facebook 帖子鼓励恐怖主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-charges-palestinian-journalist-with-encouraging-terrorism-over-online-posts/0000018c-16c3-d19a-a3cf-7ed339890000</link><description>以色列称，来自东耶路撒冷的马尔瓦特·阿扎 (Marwat Al-Azza) 撰写了有关哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的帖子，该袭击违反了恐怖主义相关法律</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 17:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-charges-palestinian-journalist-with-encouraging-terrorism-over-online-posts/0000018c-16c3-d19a-a3cf-7ed339890000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心真主党的形象，纳斯鲁拉并不急于恢复与以色列的敌对行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/fearing-for-hezbollahs-image-nasrallahs-in-no-rush-to-resume-hostilities-with-israel/0000018c-1659-dd03-a7ff-be79f8270000</link><description>什叶派民兵组织领导人哈桑·纳斯鲁拉担心，如果他再次袭击以色列，就会失去黎巴嫩公众的支持，并担心他的武装分子被迫远离以色列边境</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 15:45:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/fearing-for-hezbollahs-image-nasrallahs-in-no-rush-to-resume-hostilities-with-israel/0000018c-1659-dd03-a7ff-be79f8270000</guid></item><item><title>Satimage 显示艾森豪威尔号航母停泊在距离伊朗 100 公里的波斯湾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-28/ty-article/satimage-shows-eisenhower-carrier-in-persian-gulf-100-km-from-iran/0000018c-15f3-dab5-a7ed-97f7672a0000</link><description>艾森豪威尔号航空母舰是为威慑伊朗和真主党而部署的两艘航空母舰之一，目前位于伊朗以南 100 公里处。自哈马斯袭击开始以来，亲伊朗部队对伊拉克和叙利亚的美国目标发动了73次袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 15:21:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-28/ty-article/satimage-shows-eisenhower-carrier-in-persian-gulf-100-km-from-iran/0000018c-15f3-dab5-a7ed-97f7672a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么内塔尼亚胡如此喜爱埃隆·马斯克这样的反犹太主义者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-netanyahu-loves-antisemites-like-elon-musk-so-much/0000018c-150b-d19a-a3cf-7d9b9dd30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡一边讨好世界上最著名的犹太仇恨者，一边谴责批评者，这是在全面背叛犹太人。马斯克只是最新的危险例子，但在加沙战争期间欢迎他来到以色列尤其令人厌恶</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 15:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-netanyahu-loves-antisemites-like-elon-musk-so-much/0000018c-150b-d19a-a3cf-7d9b9dd30000</guid></item><item><title>这些以色列儿童在哈马斯袭击中幸存下来。他们努力再次成为孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-israeli-children-survived-the-hamas-attack-they-struggle-to-be-kids-again/0000018c-105f-dd2e-a5ae-d35fb8880000</link><description>“几个小时内我们就长大了好几年”：10 月 7 日事件中五名勇敢的年轻幸存者现在分散在以色列各地，讲述了在这场令人震惊的大屠杀中幸存下来的孩子们的故事</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-israeli-children-survived-the-hamas-attack-they-struggle-to-be-kids-again/0000018c-105f-dd2e-a5ae-d35fb8880000</guid></item><item><title>压力之下：以色列必须就加沙战争做出三项重大决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/under-pressure-three-fateful-decisions-israel-must-make-about-the-war-in-gaza/0000018c-1593-d19a-a3cf-7d9366eb0000</link><description>以色列在下一阶段针对加沙哈马斯的战争中面临着三大难题，其中对于内塔尼亚胡政府来说，也许没有什么比人道主义援助问题更关键和更具爆炸性了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/under-pressure-three-fateful-decisions-israel-must-make-about-the-war-in-gaza/0000018c-1593-d19a-a3cf-7d9366eb0000</guid></item><item><title>所有人的目光都集中在加沙，西岸巴勒斯坦人面临着前所未有的暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-28/ty-article-podcast/with-all-eyes-on-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-are-facing-unprecedented-violence/0000018c-11e4-dd2e-a5ae-d3ef0ac20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-28/ty-article-podcast/with-all-eyes-on-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-are-facing-unprecedented-violence/0000018c-11e4-dd2e-a5ae-d3ef0ac20000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列男子因 2021 年企图私刑处决犹太出租车司机而被判处 17 年徒刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-sentenced-to-17-years-for-attempted-lynching-of-jewish-cab-driver-in-2021/0000018c-15a9-dd2e-a5ae-d7ebb87f0000</link><description>23 岁的库赛·阿巴斯 (Qusai Abbas) 被一致判定在 2021 年 5 月以色列种族间骚乱期间与其他七名骚乱者企图谋杀莫尔·贾纳什维利 (Mor Janashvili)。法官称，一群暴徒试图处决贾纳什维利，只是因为他是犹太人</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-sentenced-to-17-years-for-attempted-lynching-of-jewish-cab-driver-in-2021/0000018c-15a9-dd2e-a5ae-d7ebb87f0000</guid></item><item><title>指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝是煽动性且危险的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza-is-inflammatory-and-dangerous/0000018c-103d-d679-abdc-963d1ecb0000</link><description>历史学家必须以事实为指导，而不是政治议程。但当《纽约时报》的奥马尔·巴托夫指责以色列“濒临”种族灭绝和种族清洗时，他的论点是基于断言，而不是证据</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 12:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza-is-inflammatory-and-dangerous/0000018c-103d-d679-abdc-963d1ecb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子因在孩子面前谋杀妻子而被判处终身监禁和六年监禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sentenced-to-life-plus-six-years-in-prison-for-murder-of-wife-in-front-of-children/0000018c-1579-dd03-a7ff-bf79aa920000</link><description>阿米尔·拉兹是一名警察，他用绳子绑住了这对夫妇的四个孩子，阻止女儿呼救，然后刺伤戴安娜并开枪射杀了她。除了谋杀之外，他还被判殴打未成年人罪名成立，法院命令他向孩子们赔偿 285,000 谢克尔</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 12:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sentenced-to-life-plus-six-years-in-prison-for-murder-of-wife-in-front-of-children/0000018c-1579-dd03-a7ff-bf79aa920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡适合在这场战争中领导以色列吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-fit-to-lead-this-war/0000018c-1584-dd2e-a5ae-d7cfbd220000</link><description>国际合法性正在迅速耗尽；与美国的紧张关系可能会爆发。但内塔尼亚胡无法应对这种复杂性。他不适合领导，必须在他的缺陷造成不可逆转的后果之前下台</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 11:41:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-fit-to-lead-this-war/0000018c-1584-dd2e-a5ae-d7cfbd220000</guid></item><item><title>几名以色列阿拉伯妇女被列入最新的囚犯名单，以换取哈马斯的释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/50-women-palestinian-prisoners-added-to-list-of-candidates-for-release-in-exchange-deal/0000018c-1532-dd03-a7ff-bf3a72ae0000</link><description>最新名单上的被拘留者中有 46 人在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后被捕。不同寻常的是，名单上的大约 20 名女性是来自该国阿拉伯社区的以色列公民，其中一些人被判犯有谋杀未遂罪</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 10:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/50-women-palestinian-prisoners-added-to-list-of-candidates-for-release-in-exchange-deal/0000018c-1532-dd03-a7ff-bf3a72ae0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔总理拒绝批评与哈马斯的关系，称此举是为了稳定该地区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/qatari-pm-rejects-criticism-over-relationship-with-hamas-says-its-to-stabilize-the-region/0000018c-1500-dd03-a7ff-bf3888480000</link><description>穆罕默德·阿勒萨尼在接受德国一家报纸采访时表示，他的国家“认同巴勒斯坦人民，而不是政党”。他补充说，正是多哈与哈马斯的联系促成了人质获释协议，并因长达数天的停火而“拯救了生命”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 10:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/qatari-pm-rejects-criticism-over-relationship-with-hamas-says-its-to-stabilize-the-region/0000018c-1500-dd03-a7ff-bf3888480000</guid></item><item><title>在对以色列立场的压力下，拜登政府强调加沙援助努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-highlights-humanitarian-aid-efforts-in-gaza-during-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-153d-d19a-a3cf-7dbd432d0000</link><description>由于白宫因支持以色列的军事目标而面临强烈批评，它现在将重点放在向加沙提供必要援助的努力上。一位官员表示，拜登、布林肯、沙利文和其他人“每天晚上都与以色列同行通电话，以解决这些问题”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 10:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-highlights-humanitarian-aid-efforts-in-gaza-during-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-153d-d19a-a3cf-7dbd432d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙正在发生的灾难：当人道主义援助成为你的最后一餐时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gazas-unfolding-disaster-when-humanitarian-aid-is-your-last-meal/0000018c-10c7-dd2e-a5ae-d3cf31b00000</link><description>孤儿在街上成倍增加，爆炸幸存者受到创伤，一旦停战结束，每个人都知道死亡随时可能再次从天而降。许多人没有药物，也几乎没有干净的水或食物</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 09:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gazas-unfolding-disaster-when-humanitarian-aid-is-your-last-meal/0000018c-10c7-dd2e-a5ae-d3cf31b00000</guid></item></channel></rss>